{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_spst_08-02","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":36,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-09_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"EG-2","storyName":"燃烧的片段2","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"关于保护的事。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_spst_08-02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"spst_08-02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":34,"next":36,"characters":["迷迭香","盾卫"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第六关（后）","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_bg_bg_topout.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"character","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"切割，穿刺，劈砍，横扫，利刃在敌人之中飞舞。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"哭喊，怒骂，诅咒，嚎叫，而后一切归于平静。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"迷迭香的表情没有任何变化。","id":13},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"解决了。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"已经没有阵地和伏击点，可以继续前进了。","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"干得漂亮，菲林。我们的人甚至还没有受伤就结束了。","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"而且，你刺穿他们头颅的速度很快，很准，很果断，这样很好。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"如果不是知道是你杀的大尉，我可能会希望你加入我们。","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你是个天生的战士，你跟着那只卡特斯，很可惜。","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"不许你说阿米娅的坏话。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"不，我并没有在批评她。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"她说了一些我很久很久以前想听，也听过的话。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"她很好，菲林，她真好。","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"但是，这行不通，菲林，这行不通。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我不信，阿米娅一定能够做到。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"或许吧，但你跟着她，对你对她都不好。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"为什么？","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你们是两类人。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"什么两类人？我和阿米娅关系很好，她教会了我许多事。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"......呵，你会懂的。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"装神弄鬼......我也不想知道。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"你刚才说，我能加入你们？","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你可以。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我们欢迎任何人。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"只要你为感染者的命运感到不公，只要你对乌萨斯感到愤怒，只要你想要战斗。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你就可以加入我们。","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你以为我们的队伍里只有乌萨斯人，只有这个国家的子民？不是的，菲林。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":50},{"type":"character","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":52},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"......你也是菲林。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我生长在雷姆必拓，随着父母来到乌萨斯，然后在这片寒冷的土地扎根。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我从小喜欢和人打架，于是后来决定参军。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"虽然乌萨斯的参军测验对菲林来说有些严苛，但我还是成功了。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"然后，我进了大尉的部队，我跟着大尉四处征战，这一打，就是十年。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"战争，紧跟着战争，还有下一场战争，这就是乌萨斯。","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我曾经为这个国家感到骄傲，孩子。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我们之中，有无数人都曾为这个国家感到骄傲。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"那么，为什么......？","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"因为我的父母感染了矿石病，被赶出了城市，死在了荒野上。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"而我甚至在他们死后的半年后才知道这件事。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"......？！","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我们之中，有无数人经历过类似的事情。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我听到你也经历了类似的事情，孩子。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"但不只是这样。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"如果只是这样，如果我只是凑巧不幸的那一个，我甚至或许可以理解。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"但是，不是这样的。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"战争曾经是我脑中唯一存在且应该完成的事业。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我在那时才开始思考一些事情，才开始去了解这个国家，去尝试理解这个我曾为之奋斗的国家。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"如果没有大尉，我可能已经因为在司令部出言不逊而进军事法庭了。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"然后，我跟着大尉走入了北原。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"而后一路走到了今天。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"在这之中，我学会了忍耐，学会了愤怒，学会了憎恨。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"......阿米娅对我说，不要学会这些。","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你总会学会的，孩子。","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"如果你不会运用它们，你就会被它们吞没。","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"所以，爱国者是你的亲人吗？","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我们共同奋战了二十年，他是我最好的兄弟，最亲的战友，最尊敬的人。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"他是，孩子。","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"但我依然要说，你更适合加入我们。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"那阿米娅能够加入你们吗？","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"那只卡特斯？不，她不行。","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"她不能加入我们。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"那我不会加入你们。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"哈，我也说了，因为你杀了大尉，你不可能加入我们了。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我不在乎。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"但要我说的话，你要多注意一下她，她想要保护你，但她可能比你死得更快。","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"为什么你这么肯定？","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058_2","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"因为我们曾经见过这样的人。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_npc_058_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"character","id":112},{"type":"text","text":"盾卫似乎回想起了什么，不再理会迷迭香，重新戴上头盔，向着他的战友走去。","id":113},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"image","id":116}],"characters":["迷迭香","盾卫"]}